{"questionId": "a7146625-47ea-49cb-9061-578e226240d5_8", "correctAnswer": "7", "section": "Math", "steps": [{"title": "Write the equation", "content": "Slope $5$, $y$-intercept $-35$: $y = 5x - 35$."}, {"title": "Set the variable $y = 0$", "content": "$0 = 5x - 35 \\Rightarrow 5x = 35 \\Rightarrow x = 7$.<br/><br/>The answer is <strong>7</strong>."}]}